'''Zdzisław Chmielewski''' (born 4 October 1942 in [[Falborz]]) is a [[Poland|Polish]] historian, rector of [[Szczecin University]], [[Member of the European Parliament]] (MEP) (elected on 13 June 2004).<ref name=usz>University of Szczecin, "Profesor Zdzisław Chmielewski – archiwista i historyk", [http://www.us.szc.pl/chmielewski/]</ref><ref>[http://www.google.com/search?hl=en&client=safari&rls=en&q=European+Parliament+Zdzisław+Chmielewski+&aq=f&aql=&aqi=&oq= European Parliament, Committee on Fisheries]</ref>

